      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Cidel$<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>...?<BR>
Well... I've never heard of it before....<BR>
If you want, I can ask the natives...</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n707_sidel-1-b" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n707_sidel-2" mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Hey, did you just say <FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>?!<BR>You should ask <FONT color=#a82424>Doctor</FONT> about such things!<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>(Doctors shouts while flapping his pages)</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n707_sidel-2" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>$Cidel$<BR>That's great. <FONT color=#a82424>Doctor</FONT> must know something about the Mirror of Truth.<BR>
Let's go and see.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-a" mid="20"><![CDATA[<html>(Look at the records)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Let's see.<BR>Hmm.... Truth or dare... not this. Truth of lie... not this either. The inconvenient truth? Not this. What the heck is the sword of truth....<BR>The Mirror of Tr... Oh, it's here.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-a" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-b" mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Mirror of Truth$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>The long War of the Ancients ended with the </FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>Evil Ancients' Leader</FONT><FONT color=#7e12d2> being caught. The leader had evil energy spread all over his body and his original good self could not be found.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-b" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-c" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Mirror of Truth$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>The good ancients tried their best to return him to his good self. However, they failed after many tries.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-c" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-d" mid="39"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="38"><![CDATA[<html>$Mirror of Truth$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>Opinions about how to deal with him was split.</FONT><BR>
<FONT color=#7e12d2>If Nereid did not find the Mirror of Truth, he would have been recorded as the evil man who had thrust the world into chaos.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-d" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-e" mid="45"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="42"><![CDATA[<html>$Mirror of Truth$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>The leader of the evil ancients, Bishas Arnobius.</FONT><BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>Wise Arno, who was Nereid's lover and the saviour of the world who single-handedly defeated the Black Dragon, could return to his good self again.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-e" image="QN_Npc_BookDoc.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-f" mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="46"><![CDATA[<html>$Mirror of Truth$<BR><FONT color=#7e12d2>The evil spirit that was used to control Wise Arno was sealed deeply inside the Mirror of Truth. Nereid decided to hide the mirror somewhere in the Encroached Temple Ruins until the evil energy was neutralized and dissolved.</FONT></html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-f" image="QW_62.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-g" mid="26"><![CDATA[<html>Encroached Temple Ruins...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Hmm... according to the records, the place where you can find the Mirror of Truth is <FONT color=#a82424>Encroached Temple Ruins</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-g" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400321">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-h" mid="28"><![CDATA[<html>Then how can I find it...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Yes. The important thing is that only those with a fake self can see the <FONT color=#a82424>Mirror of Truth</FONT>.<BR>Those who are their true self can't see nor feel the mirror.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-h" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-i" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>What? How...?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Since the fake ones can see it, you can change yourself into a fake self.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-i" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="400320">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-2-j" mid="32"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>Why do I need to explain every single thing....<BR>You can use <FONT color=#a82424>Mask of Distortion</FONT>.<BR>You can make it by using meteor fragments and mutated eye.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-2-j" image="" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n703_book_doctor-3" mid="34"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>If you wear that mask, the Mirror of Truth will see you as a fake one, so you'll be able to see the Mirror of Truth.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n703_book_doctor-3" image="QW_63.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="50"><![CDATA[<html>$Chatterbox Book Doctor$<BR>First, go and find the materials needed to make the mask of distortion.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Meteor fragment</FONT> can be found at <FONT color=#a82424>Meteor Crash Site Core</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
